you that I don't have a job?

31:26.607 --> 31:27.767
I don't care.

31:28.642 --> 31:29.870
I want you to come anyway.

31:35.683 --> 31:37.708
- Think you can remember?
- Of course.

31:39.553 --> 31:40.178
How?

31:40.955 --> 31:41.922
Well...

