32:35.776 --> 32:36.765
Earnest Johnson!

32:37.478 --> 32:39.309
- Yes?
- Kate Madison.

32:40.114 --> 32:41.206
- Hi, there.
- Hi.

32:43.918 --> 32:46.352
Shit! You're the lady
from the news.

32:46.420 --> 32:48.718
